metadata.description: On a mission to save the original spicy taste and protect the world from disgusting and unhealthy fast food giants. Our members will be freed from the clutches of fast-food damnation and set out to protect the planet from low quality pizza, burgers and hot dogs. The unique digital collectibles live in the Taco Force with a mission to rid the world and its people of terrible food. By consuming bad food, humans mutate into smaller monsters and subsequently lower their life expectancy by at least a few years. The five squads of the Taco Force, led by their battalions, have to prove their team spirit in order to acquire better skills, equipment, and suits. ITâ€™S TACO TIME!!!!!!!
